{"tid":222953,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"【新手填詞自唱】《初戀》By青如 (求婚大作戰X步步驚心麗)","createTime":"2017-04-30T03:12:47.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-02T07:52:05.000Z","uid":35370,"like":10,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"e3d04abf8d3c94cebcf730ca44a4c064731353a8","tid":222953,"uid":35370,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-30T03:12:47.000Z","msg":"YOUTUBE片如下： <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?feature=youtu.be&amp;v=N0GuvwEfskI\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Ffeature%3Dyoutu.be%26v%3DN0GuvwEfskI&d=eUEb8trTAlhqW9E3j8wilywN645TRhVPBLeqKBQ2Igw%3D&h=48b28fab\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?feature=youtu.be&amp;v=N0GuvwEfskI</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n由填詞到整好mv錄好音<br />\n用咗加埋9個鐘左右嘅時間（因為之後唔得閒再搞）<br />\n希望大家見諒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />快工出劣貨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">亦因為趕住出所以搵自己呢個唔識唱歌嘅人嚟唱住先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong>原曲： 步步驚心-麗 OST<br />\nA Lot Like Love - Baek A Yeon<br />\n<br />\n填詞： 青如<br />\n翻唱： 青如<br />\n<br />\n歌詞：</strong><br />\n<br />\n我想重回當初 無限次邂逅<br />\n那種感覺 仍永帶興奮<br />\n到今天 尋不到 若可再相見<br />\n你會否知道 你存在我心坎<br />\n若我當天可知其實時間 不可等待<br />\n明白再會也是要靠福氣 怎麼會<br />\n<br />\n* 尚會憶起當天曾經跌倒 抬頭時<br />\n是你 低谷中拉起我手 友善<br />\n沒有講愛你麼 哪管沒道理<br />\n但是原來是我 做錯<br />\n<br />\n上早會 插班生 陌生的笑容<br />\n我怎麼想到 後來坐我身邊<br />\n沒法阻擋心中無限愁緒 今天湧現<br />\n如若再會結局會否改變 HA<br />\n<br />\n即使身邊 無論多少 俊或美<br />\n但心中我知 怎可比<br />\n還記得 對你說過 永遠不散 沒有別與離<br />\n還是欠勇氣 說一聲 I love you<br />\n<br />\n沒法猜測今天如此結果 誰明瞭<br />\n是我怕尷尬鬆開你手 幼稚<br />\n願這刻 轉過身 看到就是你<br />\n心中祈求上帝 讓我<br />\n望重頭來過 做妥<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n係咁先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />希望各位手下留情<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"432556a1cd7a910a26eb914bc64e5ee45cfbe4a5","tid":222953,"uid":63452,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-30T03:16:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"35114d2757096c1f2a27ff7d10a135a8b76c8529","tid":222953,"uid":35370,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-30T03:21:55.000Z","msg":"BTW 段片可能有廣告<br />\n但唔係我本人落嘅，而係因為我個bgm用咗原聲帶<br />\nYoutube搵到我用咗，話原聲帶間公司可能係我段片落度廣告<br />\n希望大家唔好介意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1c7794ab453fc95d0e73cfe1685ac2e7483f4621","tid":222953,"uid":35370,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-30T03:25:09.000Z","msg":"原曲係咁樣嘅：<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/qvis0D9wYTg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fqvis0D9wYTg&d=eUEb8trTAlhqW9E3j8wilywN645TRhVPBLeqKBQ2Igw%3D&h=11c6c973\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/qvis0D9wYTg</a>"},{"pid":"9cc6d6ca4ec332658a82b9a7940d661cc2c5d06b","tid":222953,"uid":40429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-30T03:25:47.000Z","msg":"絲打唱得好好<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/pokemon_2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0521ba73c3952e0755de73ab2ae5d10791f4696a","tid":222953,"uid":35370,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-30T03:43:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>絲打唱得好好<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/pokemon_2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n多謝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"64d25432f4022135711678eb5a956e5c38608e92","tid":222953,"uid":63452,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-30T04:09:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f7d6bc934c5228e05dfa33d3177b476cc1ee4d07","tid":222953,"uid":1086,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-30T05:00:25.000Z","msg":"搵支好咪"},{"pid":"8e7ee80db32d732cae8b04d942989a4907d408eb","tid":222953,"uid":35370,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"ci